wind blown snow
<br>
a ewe&#8217;s cry
<br>
in the night
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Angela Terry
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM4></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>
mild winter
<br>
the shore ice
<br>
releases its litter
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Hilary Tann 
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM6></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>
measuring a life
