to crocus
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Beth McFarland
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM8></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>
songbirds returning . . .
<br>
the tunes my father
<br>
would whistle
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Francine Banwarth
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM10></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>
trail frog
<br>
the children
<br>
jump back
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
John Hawk
